1
00:01:04,886 --> 00:01:07,721
My dear Frodo:

2
00:01:13,269 --> 00:01:19,608
You asked me once if I had told you everything
there was to know about my adventures.

3
00:01:19,775 --> 00:01:23,528
And while I can honestly say
I have told you the truth...

4
00:01:24,780 --> 00:01:27,032
...I may not have told you all of it.

5
00:01:35,082 --> 00:01:37,125
I am old now, Frodo.

6
00:01:38,628 --> 00:01:41,379
I'm not the same Hobbit I once was.

7
00:01:44,675 --> 00:01:49,179
I think it is time for you to know...

8
00:01:49,347 --> 00:01:52,015
...what really happened.

